<i>&gt;It's nice to have a directory of addresses.  However, I think it would</i><br>
<i>&gt;be nice to have information on the what people are studying.  I know a</i><br>
<i>&gt;number of subscribers are in the computer/technology field.  Anyone out</i><br>
