<p>
I work with as a Sr. Database Engineer with Cellular Technical Services, in <br>
Seattle, Washington.  CTS is a company that provides services to the cellular<br>
industry.  Our software allows the cellular providers to monitor usage and <br>
catch phones involved in fraudulent activities.<br>
<p>
I am personally involved with data dictionary design, DBA activities, and<br>
4GL programming.  There is a little bit of programming that I am responsible<br>
for in C.<br>
<p>
I have been working with databases, user interfaces, their design and coding<br>
all of my professional life (10+ years).  It is an exciting field and I <br>
enjoy it greatly.<br>
<p>
Let me know a little more about yourself.<br>
<p>
Russell Grau<br>
