Steve<br>
<p>
I have just a few comments on your listing of Canadian Union College in<br>
"SDA Colleges on the net."  The Director of Computer Services is<br>
currently exploring several options that would permit the college to<br>
have Internet access.  This may take several months.  However, I will<br>
share the results when this is achieved.<br>
<p>
You have listed me under the heading of the college.  I should point<br>
out that my involvement in SDAnet is personal, not institutional.  <br>
However, until the college establishes an Internet link, I will be<br>
pleased to channel any messages to CaUC students, faculty, or staff.<br>
<p>
Finally, let me correct a minor matter.  While I still teach one course<br>
in the Department of Religious Studies, my primary appointment is<br>
Vice-President (Academic).<br>
<p>
Warren C. Trenchard<br>
