<i>&gt; [A message from Sherman Cox]</i><br>
<i>&gt; 	I would like to know if anyone has read the book "Inspiration" by</i><br>
<i>&gt; Alden Thompson.</i><br>
<p>
Just finished it.<br>
<p>
Need to go through it again, at least one more time.<br>
<p>
I thought it was excellent.<br>
<p>
<i>&gt; In it he talks of the implications of our belief</i><br>
<i>&gt; in thought inspiration.  I believe sometimes we as adventists give</i><br>
<i>&gt; lip service to the idea of thought inspiration, but in reality when</i><br>
<i>&gt; we speak about our ideas it realy is verbal inspiration.</i><br>
<p>
Occasionally, some of us lean too far in the other direction...but<br>
either stance has problems.<br>
