<title>Jan_1993: SDA-L: Updated Directory, one more time</title>
<h1>SDA-L: Updated Directory, one more time</h1>
Steven Timm (<i>st0o+%ANDREW.CMU.EDU%CMU.EDU@bitnet.cc.cmu.edu</i>)<br>
