<title>Jan_1993: sources for OnLine Bible (excellent PC freeware)</title>
<h1>sources for OnLine Bible (excellent PC freeware)</h1>
Fred Christiansen (<i>fredch@phx.mcd.mot.com</i>)<br>
<i>Fri, 22 Jan 93 13:40:20 MST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#90">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#90">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#90">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#90">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0091.html">Gilbert Bailey: "Inspiration/Interpretation"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0089.html">Sherman Cox: "inspiration"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
