<!-- body="start" -->
I've received several requests for sources for the OnLine Bible software<br>
following my posting about it some weeks back.  I've recently located<br>
two sources:<br>
	Premium Software	1-800-723-0658<br>
		(part of their Bible Bundle, 16 disks, $24.99)<br>
	Reasonable Solutions	1-800-876-3475<br>
<p>
Make sure they have version 6.00 or higher (5.00 is ok, but you might as<br>
well have the latest).  The cost is for the diskettes.  Since it's freeware,<br>
there's nothing more to pay.  The reason it's free is that its developers<br>
and contributors are all volunteers (like the Free Software Foundation,<br>
for any of you Unix types).<br>
<pre>
-- 
Fred Christiansen, Motorola, 2900 S Diablo Way, Tempe, AZ 85282  "Canajun, eh?"
fredch@phx.mcd.mot.com  ||  uunet!phx.mcd.mot.com!fredch  ||  +1 602-438-3464
  ".. I have set before you Life and Death, blessing and cursing;  therefore
      choose Life, that both you and your children may live"  Deut 30:19
</pre>
