Two environmental issues I can think of are drug/alcohol abuse and social gangs.\<br>
Although view primarily as social issues rather than environmental, the empty<br>
alcohol containers, dirty needles and other drug paraphenalia are environmental<br>
hazards and pollute the earth.  Gangs are the primary destroyers of inner city<br>
buildings with graffiti, gang warfare, etc.<br>
<p>
Cheryl<br>
