Several people have suggested to me privately that I should read the book<br>
"God Cares" by Mervyn Maxwell, which speaks to the issue I raised about <br>
Daniel 9:24-27 this morning.  I am aware that this book is one of several <br>
good books on the topic.  Unfortunately, I don't have these books,<br>
nor do I have access to a library where they are, nor do I have money or time<br>
to buy them at my friendly local A.B.C. which closes at 5PM every night.<br>
<p>
So could someone be a friend and encapsulate Maxwell's argument on the <br>
question of why the seventieth week must follow the other 69?  I'd be <br>
ever so obliged.  <br>
<p>
Steve Timm<br>
