<title>Jan_1993: Re: KJV - historical Adventist's bible</title>
<h1>Re: KJV - historical Adventist's bible</h1>
Bruce Holm (<i>bruceh@wv.mentorg.com</i>)<br>
<i>Thu, 28 Jan 93 09:58:49 -0800</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#125">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#125">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#125">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#125">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0126.html">Ruben Gonzalez: "Historical Adventism and the environment"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0124.html">PHTH1@cc.newcastle.edu.au: "Historical Adventism and the environment"</a>
<li> <b>Maybe in reply to:</b> <a href="0117.html">PHTH1@cc.newcastle.edu.au: "KJV - historical Adventist's bible"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
