the whole body of text from the message to which they are responding.<br>
I would ask you to please keep this practice to a minimum.  Only <br>
include the lines that you are specifically responding to.  Remember <br>
that for some people (including myself) mail takes up real disk quota.<br>
<p>
Steve Timm<br>
