<title>Jan_1993: Australia</title>
<h1>Australia</h1>
Sherman Cox (<i>scox@uahcs2.cs.uah.edu</i>)<br>
<i>Fri, 29 Jan 93 8:34:26 CST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#139">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#139">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#139">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#139">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0140.html">Woody Baker: "Re: KJV - historical Adventist's bible"</a>
