<title>Jan_1993: Re: Historical Adventism and the environment</title>
<h1>Re: Historical Adventism and the environment</h1>
Malcolm Butler (<i>malb@boojum.ee.uts.edu.au</i>)<br>
<i>Fri, 29 Jan 93 16:17:14 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#141">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#141">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#141">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#141">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0142.html">Steven Timm: "Bible versions"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0140.html">Woody Baker: "Re: KJV - historical Adventist's bible"</a>
