<title>Jan_1993: Re: Australia</title>
<h1>Re: Australia</h1>
Malcolm Butler (<i>malb@boojum.ee.uts.edu.au</i>)<br>
<i>Sun, 31 Jan 93 2:20:41 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#148">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#148">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#148">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#148">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0149.html">cheryl berthelsen: "Death and escape from death"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0147.html">ARKUSINSKI ANDY : "PERSONAL INFO"</a>
<li> <b>In reply to:</b> <a href="0139.html">Sherman Cox: "Australia"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
