looks natural and jewelry in good taste -- not in excess. I know what you<br>
mean by excess though -- rings on all fingers, 6 or more necklaces at a<br>
time, couple of bracelets on each arm and enough makeup to look like a<br>
clown! My wife is a clown incidently, and has done a lot of birthday<br>
parties etc. She calls herself "Angel The Clown" and for the part wears<br>
and spears a lot of makeup on to look the part. But, she doesn't wear that<br>
much makeup when she is wearing "street clothes" or even to church!!<br>
&lt;&lt;smile!&gt;&gt;<br>
