<title>Aug_1992: Who's in charge?</title>
<h1>Who's in charge?</h1>
Dan Blake (<i>dblake@hprnd.rose.hp.com</i>)<br>
<i>Tue, 25 Aug 92 17:36:27 PDT</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#47">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#47">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#47">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#47">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0048.html">Ian Brown: "Adventist Education"</a>
