Two or three times within the last month I have received responses to <br>
posts which never went through me.  I can only assume that people <br>
are replying to private E-mail to the whole net.  Please check to <br>
see where a message came from before sending a reply back to the net.<br>
<p>
Thanks,<br>
<p>
Steve Timm<br>
