<title>Aug_1992: Re: Who's in charge?</title>
<h1>Re: Who's in charge?</h1>
Steven Timm (<i>st0o+@andrew.cmu.edu</i>)<br>
<i>Wed, 26 Aug 1992 21:56:56 -0400 (EDT)</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#55">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#55">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#55">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#55">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0056.html">Tony: "Re: The minister's wife - what's her name again?"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0054.html">Tony: "Re: Who's in charge?"</a>
<li> <b>In reply to:</b> <a href="0054.html">Tony: "Re: Who's in charge?"</a>
