Lisa Parry (<i>parry@gandalf.cs.andrews.edu</i>)<br>
<i>Fri, 28 Aug 92 12:44:59 EDT</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#67">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#67">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#67">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#67">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0068.html">Fred Christiansen: "Re: Religious liberty on University campuses"</a>
