<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0073.html">Steven Timm: "Re: Rules and Culture"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0071.html">Dan Blake: "Re: The minister's wife"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
