Hi, Steve,<br>
<p>
Do I smell a chicken-or-egg type of cause-effect problem arising?<br>
<p>
Do we have to start healing the individual before healing families,<br>
as Cheryl suggests, or healing the family before healing individuals?<br>
<p>
The pragmatic thing to do is try to "solve" both problems at the <br>
same time. But it sounds too easy. <br>
<p>
OK, Bible scholars and psych majors, go at it! :)<br>
