It may be true that the main participants in this discussion do not<br>
change their views very much.  But I think there are many people<br>
sitting on the sidelines who may not have thought about these issues<br>
much before.  For them especially I think this discussion can be useful,<br>
especially since the presentations I have seen in denominational<br>
publications do not make the issues clear, perhaps in order to avoid<br>
controversy.<br>
<p>
	Dave Plaisted<br>
