<title>Oct_1992: Re:  Discussion on perfection</title>
<h1>Re:  Discussion on perfection</h1>
Steven Timm (<i>st0o+@andrew.cmu.edu</i>)<br>
<i>Mon,  5 Oct 1992 21:23:06 -0400 (EDT)</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#19">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#19">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#19">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#19">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0020.html">Steven Timm: "Praying for the gift of tongues"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0018.html">David Plaisted: "discussion on perfection"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
