<p>
Bill writes :<br>
<p>
<i>&gt;My view of PERFECTION is that of continued CHRISTIAN MATURITY.  Whatever</i><br>
<i>&gt;good is there to be done that I am aware of, I should do it.  Jesus' </i><br>
