<title>Oct_1992: Giving</title>
<h1>Giving</h1>
Nancy Vyhmeister (<i>vyhmeist@edmund.cs.andrews.edu</i>)<br>
<i>Thu, 8 Oct 92 9:42:25 EDT</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#34">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#34">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#34">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#34">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0035.html">Tony: "Re: School choice"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0033.html">Steven Timm: "Strings Attached (School Choice)"</a>
