<title>Oct_1992: Who is Michael the archangel?</title>
<h1>Who is Michael the archangel?</h1>
Dan Blake (<i>dblake@hprnd.rose.hp.com</i>)<br>
<i>Fri, 9 Oct 92 18:20:19 PDT</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#39">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#39">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#39">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#39">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
