personal e-mail.<br>
<p>
<i>&gt; Jesus (in his role as Michael, the archangel)...</i><br>
<p>
Would anyone care to comment on the identity of Michael?<br>
<p>
Thanks,<br>
<p>
Dan Blake<br>
