FYI,<br>
<p>
When I attended Bill Gothard's Youth Conference in 1982, he was unmarried,<br>
had never been married, and had never been a father.  This was the very<br>
reason many people questioned his approach to the family because he had\<br>
never experienced or tried them himself.  Any new report you may remember<br>
hearing in 1979/80 could not have been accurate.<br>
