Please forgive me if this is a bit messy.  We have mentally ill person who<br>
has been attending some of our Sabbath services and has been disturbing<br>
some of the people, particularlly at pot luck.  At the most recent board<br>
meeting one member mentioned how if he came back they wanted him sent<br>
away.  The man who comes is schizonphrenic probably and obviously very<br>
very paranoid.  He has been by here before, and we have helped him to get<br>
where  he wanted to go at least once.  I have been trying to think of<br>
something meaningful we could do for the man, but I am at a loss.    Any<br>
recommendations? <br>
<p>
Ian.<br>
