I attended a Bill Gothard seminar around 20 years ago.  I enjoyed it.  I<br>
have not attended one since however.  I don't know the status of Bill's<br>
ministry, but I do know that it must still be active to some extent as<br>
I have received a birthday card from it consistently for the last twenty<br>
years including two months ago.  I would conclude that his ministry must<br>
still be active.<br>
<p>
--Cam Litvin  PROFS Support  CLLITVIN<br>
