Steve<br>
<p>
There is a group of independent ministries (I believe) who call<br>
themselves "Light Bearers" and have been publishing a lot of literature<br>
and distributing extensively especially here in Africa . I believe one<br>
of their members is a man by the name of T. Gibson .<br>
<p>
I just wanted to know about their relationship to the Church now as I am<br>
made to understand through a document issured by the Bible Research<br>
Institute in 1989 (May I think) that their work was not endorsed by the<br>
Church .<br>
<p>
Help on this issue would be greatly appreciated as it has caused a lot<br>
of mis-understandings within churches here , especially in Harare , with<br>
members not sure whether their literature should be distributed in the<br>
name of the Church .<br>
<p>
Colin<br>
(cchibafa@zimbix.uz.zw)<br>
