<title>Oct_1992: Re:  Questions on the Trinity</title>
<h1>Re:  Questions on the Trinity</h1>
Steven Timm (<i>st0o+@andrew.cmu.edu</i>)<br>
<i>Thu, 15 Oct 1992 11:49:59 -0400 (EDT)</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#79">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#79">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#79">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#79">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0080.html">Eric Snyder: "The Trinity"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0078.html">Raylene: "Different people in our churches"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
