Hi all,<br>
<p>
Now personally, I have not worried too much about this issue yet,<br>
seeing as I haven't needed to.<br>
<p>
Yet I believe it is significant that Jesus and John the Baptist were<br>
both  home-schooled. In fact the rest of his brothers and the priests <br>
often complained to Mary that Jesus was out of line for not attending <br>
the synagogue schools.<br>
<p>
Was Jesus' time really all that different from now ?<br>
<p>
Ruben.<br>
<!-- body="end" -->
