Ty Gibson and Light Bearers used to catch a lot of conference flack<br>
for accepting tithe and so were banned from church pulpits, for<br>
example in the Oregon Conference.  Recently they came to terms with<br>
their local conference and issued a letter announcing that they<br>
would no longer accept tithe.  Soon after that the Oregon Conference<br>
took them off the "black list".<br>
<p>
DaveB<br>
