Fred Kinsey, Communications Director of the Northern California Conference, <br>
has a desire to begin a Seventh-day Adventist Forum on Compuserve. This would <br>
be a place where not only messages could be placed but articles from Union <br>
papers could be downloaded along with software, graphics, or other items of <br>
potential interest.<br>
<p>
If there is a great deal of support for the idea it would help to pursuade <br>
Compuserve it would be worth it. Also Fred could probably use help setting it <br>
up. Any interest can be forwarded to him at Compuserve address 71340,3037.<br>
<p>
Ed Fargusson (Compuserve 72450,2430)<br>
