<title>Oct_1992: Re: Michael the archangel</title>
<h1>Re: Michael the archangel</h1>
Tony (<i>72450.2430@compuserve.com</i>)<br>
<i>15 Oct 92 13:54:11 EDT</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#89">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#89">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#89">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#89">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0090.html">cheryl berthelsen: "High School Church Programs"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0088.html">Tony: "SDA Forum on Compuserve"</a>
<li> <b>Maybe in reply to:</b> <a href="0042.html">Ian Brown: "Michael the archangel"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
