<title>Oct_1992: Re: SDA Forum on Compuserve</title>
<h1>Re: SDA Forum on Compuserve</h1>
Daniel Turk (<i>turk@peter.cs.andrews.edu</i>)<br>
<i>Fri, 16 Oct 92 19:59:53 EDT</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#93">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#93">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#93">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#93">[ author ]</a>
