A couple of weeks ago, Ian posted summaries of the two articles<br>
listed below.  I shared those summaries with a friend who has spent<br>
a considerable time studying I John and is now teaching a class on<br>
it.  He has become very interested in reading the original articles.<br>
Can anyone help me acquire them?  We live near Sacramento, California.<br>
Is there a local archive?  I would be happy to reimburse someone at<br>
Andrews for copying and mailing charges.<br>
<p>
Thank you,<br>
<p>
Dan Blake  &lt;dblake@hprnd.rose.hp.com&gt;<br>
