<!-- body="start" -->
to Network:<br>
<p>
Tony: <br>
<p>
I understand what you are saying about men --- very simple, no makeup etc.<br>
<p>
Whether we wear makeup or not -- whether a wedding ring or not --- really<br>
are minor issues. However, some church members make them major.  Just who<br>
was it that coined the expression, "majoring on minors?"!!!!<br>
<p>
I am also reminded that the General Conf. committee spent 3 days talking<br>
about the wedding ring!  Really now, is that necessary?? Are we being good<br>
stewards of our time???!!  &lt;&lt;smile!&gt;&gt;<br>
<p>
........Paul<br>
