Hi, Greater SDA-L<br>
(which includes SDA-L members and all people who receive it's echo through<br>
SDAnet.)<br>
<p>
You notice that I'm titling the subject header of all things I send through<br>
SDA-L with SDA-L:, this way people can tell the difference easily as<br>
to what net the message went over and reply appropriately.<br>
<p>
Here is the directory of all members of both lists, as far as I know.<br>
If you want more information by your name, please E-mail me, or post to the<br>
list and let everyone know.<br>
<p>
SDA-L and SDAnet membership information as of Sep 1, 1992<br>
<p>
This information is for SDA-L and SDAnet members usage only.  Misuse will<br>
not be tolerated.<br>
<p>
By my count there are 127 working addresses in greater SDA-L right now, this<br>
includes the overlap of those people signed up to both SDA-L and SDAnet.<br>
