<title>Sep_1992: Re:  Sat v. Sun Sabbath</title>
<h1>Re:  Sat v. Sun Sabbath</h1>
cheryl berthelsen (<i>cherylb@csd4.csd.uwm.edu</i>)<br>
<i>Wed, 2 Sep 92 14:23:28 -0500</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#24">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#24">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#24">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#24">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0025.html">cheryl berthelsen: "Re: SDA-L:  Directory of all current members"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0023.html">cheryl berthelsen: "Re:  Sat v. Sun Sabbath"</a>
<li> <b>Maybe in reply to:</b> <a href="0015.html">Scott Mattes: "Sat v. Sun Sabbath"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
<li> <b>Next in thread:</b> <a href="0039.html">Bill Oblitey: "Re: Sat v. Sun Sabbath"</a>
</ul>
<!-- body="start" -->
