Network,<br>
Lola, <br>
<p>
Glad the temple plan is working. I think I pastored one of the last<br>
churches in Mich. that used the Temple Plan. That was the Grand Ledge<br>
church. I pastored there for 8 years and I could see the problems<br>
increasing year by year. Some parents with 2 or 3 children were paying<br>
$5.00 a month or none at all into church expense. What we finally did was<br>
get a commitment from the parents of what they could give each month and<br>
then we got sponsors from the church to make up the difference.<br>
<p>
Before we did that 90% of our church budget was going to the school. When<br>
we needed to make repairs to church and even just routine mainatenance we<br>
couldn't do it because so much of the budget was going to the academy<br>
across the street.<br>
<p>
........Paul<br>
<!-- body="end" -->
