<title>Sep_1992: Re: Response to Tony's question about vegetarianism</title>
<h1>Re: Response to Tony's question about vegetarianism</h1>
Paul Gates (<i>70516.420@compuserve.com</i>)<br>
<i>03 Sep 92 01:41:20 EDT</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#34">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#34">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#34">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#34">[ author ]</a>
