<title>Sep_1992: Re: re: Rules and Culture</title>
<h1>Re: re: Rules and Culture</h1>
Paul Gates (<i>70516.420@compuserve.com</i>)<br>
<i>03 Sep 92 01:41:35 EDT</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#36">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#36">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#36">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#36">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0037.html">Drew Corrigan: "Easter, Christmas and Festivals"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0035.html">Paul Gates: "Re: Address for Biblical Research Inst."</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
