<title>Sep_1992: Music ideas</title>
<h1>Music ideas</h1>
Steven Timm (<i>st0o+@andrew.cmu.edu</i>)<br>
<i>Thu,  3 Sep 1992 09:23:01 -0400 (EDT)</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#42">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#42">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#42">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#42">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0043.html">Lisa Parry: "Wedding Band"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0041.html">Paul Gates: "SABBATH"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
<li> <b>Next in thread:</b> <a href="0048.html">Stan Macasieb: "Re: Music ideas"</a>
