<title>Sep_1992: Re: Day of rest</title>
<h1>Re: Day of rest</h1>
Fred Christiansen (<i>fredch@phx.mcd.mot.com</i>)<br>
<i>Thu, 3 Sep 92 10:16:31 MST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#52">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#52">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#52">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#52">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0053.html">Adam David: "Re:  Sat v. Sun Sabbath"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0051.html">Paul Gates: "Sabbath/ Salvation"</a>
