<p>
Dave,<br>
Take the initiative.  Start a Mid-week prayer meeting or a Friday night<br>
discussion and prayer group and seen how it goes with the students.<br>
Then invite the "leaders" to come and join or give presentations after<br>
which discussions would follow.  Make sure you control the topics for<br>
discussions.<br>
We did this at the University of Ghana and I believe it's still going on<br>
with the students over there.<br>
<p>
Bill Oblitey<br>
[OBLITEY@OAK.GROVE.IUP.EDU]<br>
