<title>Sep_1992: plant suffering</title>
<h1>plant suffering</h1>
Dave Plaisted (<i>st0o+@andrew.cmu.edu</i>)<br>
<i>Fri,  4 Sep 1992 15:42:02 -0400 (EDT)</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#65">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#65">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#65">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#65">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0066.html">Tim Swensen: "students ... addendum"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0064.html">David Plaisted: "vegetarianism"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
<li> <b>Next in thread:</b> <a href="0075.html">Dan Blake: "Re: plant suffering"</a>
