<h1>Re: Day of rest</h1>
Paul Gates (<i>70516.420@compuserve.com</i>)<br>
<i>04 Sep 92 19:29:21 EDT</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#71">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#71">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#71">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#71">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0072.html">Paul Gates: "Re: Christian Nation"</a>
