<h1>Re: plant suffering</h1>
Dan Blake (<i>dblake@hprnd.rose.hp.com</i>)<br>
<i>Fri, 4 Sep 92 17:57:32 PDT</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#75">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#75">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#75">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#75">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0076.html">Steven Timm: "Modern prophets and the Sabbath"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0074.html">Paul Gates: "Re: Wedding Band"</a>
