<title>Sep_1992: New Greater SDA-L Directory</title>
<h1>New Greater SDA-L Directory</h1>
Steven Timm (<i>st0o+%ANDREW.CMU.EDU%CMU.EDU@bitnet.cc.cmu.edu</i>)<br>
<i>07 Sep 1992 14:37:15 -0400</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#82">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#82">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#82">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#82">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0083.html">Steven Timm: "SDA-L:  Let the personals begin"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0081.html">Steven Timm: "A record week"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
</ul>
<!-- body="start" -->
SDA-L and SDAnet membership information as of Sep 07, 1992<br>
<p>
This information is for SDA-L and SDAnet members usage only.  Misuse will<br>
not be tolerated.<br>
<p>
93 working addresses are signed up to SDAnet right now, and 37 other working<br>
addresses are signed up to SDA-L but not SDAnet.<br>
<p>
Any directory changes or questions about either list should go to me.<br>
<p>
<p>
Lola Aagaard                  AAGAARD@MOREKYPR                           BOTH<br>
     Lola lives in Morehead, Kentucky<br>
<p>
Andy Arkusinski               arkusinski@swdev.si.com                  SDAnet<br>
     Andy is a computer programmer in Grand Rapids, MI.<br>
<p>
Vijay Balasingam              EDUMED124@MEDCOR.MCGILL.CA                SDA-L<br>
