Sunday. In fact I understand the Book of Mormon was a revelation, or<br>
could I use the phrase, "prophetic messages" for North America just like<br>
the prophets in the OT &amp; NT received messages for Bible lands in Bible<br>
times.<br>
<p>
Adventist members are not that fortunate with Ellen White. Even though she<br>
did have revelations and visions everything she says seemingly point back<br>
to the Holy Bible or the scriptures. In fact EGW said one time that if the<br>
people would really study the scriptures they would not need her writings.<br>
That is really something isn't it?<br>
