<title>Sep_1992: students and food</title>
<h1>students and food</h1>
Lola (<i>AAGAARD%morekypr.BITNET@bitnet.cc.cmu.edu</i>)<br>
<i>07 Sep 1992 17:33:20 -0400 (EDT)</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#99">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#99">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#99">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#99">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0100.html">Lola: "Re: LOST TIME"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0098.html">Tony: "Scripture &amp; prophets"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
