<title>Sep_1992: Re: Vegetarianism</title>
<h1>Re: Vegetarianism</h1>
Paul (<i>st0o+@andrew.cmu.edu</i>)<br>
<i>Thu, 10 Sep 1992 22:00:53 -0400 (EDT)</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#125">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#125">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#125">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#125">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0126.html">Ruben Gonzalez: "Re:  God's Law portrays His character?"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0124.html">Dan Blake: "Re: 1994"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
