<title>Sep_1992: Re: Translation Faith</title>
<h1>Re: Translation Faith</h1>
Ruben Gonzalez (<i>ruben@ee.uts.edu.au</i>)<br>
<i>Fri, 11 Sep 92 13:55:28 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#128">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#128">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#128">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#128">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0129.html">Ian Brown: "New Jerusalem and 1000 years"</a>
