This 1994 date for the Second Coming is not new.  We had a professor in the<br>
Philippines teach it in his Bible classes.  He got it from the 6000 years<br>
beginning with Usher's 4004 chronology.  Several of his students quit school<br>
and went out to an isolated village where they had a day and night retreat,<br>
preparing to go out and preach.  After a few months most of them quietly<br>
came back.  The professor decided that since the board told him to desist <br>
from promulgating his views or cease receiving a salary, he would change his<br>
mind.  Just a story...<br>
Nancy<br>
<!-- body="end" -->
