that singles-type notices appear in the list.  Obviously when people<br>
are in e-mail communication similarities of interest will take their<br>
own course and singles will get acquainted.  However, the suggestion<br>
that as a third or fourth priority this list could directly serve that<br>
prupose appears to be an error in judgement.  Think about it.<br>
