<h1>SDA-L:  Personals</h1>
Steven Timm (<i>st0o+%ANDREW.CMU.EDU%CMU.EDU@bitnet.cc.cmu.edu</i>)<br>
<i>16 Sep 1992 08:57:46 -0400</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#150">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#150">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#150">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#150">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0151.html">Lisa Parry: "SDA-L response"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0149.html">Jeff Tosk: "LET ME OFF THIS LIST"</a>
