Since I was wishing people wouldn't be so shy, guess I'll put a bio in too.<br>
<p>
I'm Lisa Parry (white single female if those are important), closing in on 21<br>
(just a few more days).  I'm graduating from Andrews University next June with<br>
BA's in Math and Computer Science, planning to teach on the secondary level<br>
(in a church run school if possible, though currently I'm part time for the<br>
local public school system).<br>
<p>
I've lived quite a few places in the US, ranging from Maine to Texas to<br>
Utah including a few others.<br>
<p>
Grew up in an Adventist home, but really discovered Jesus for myself during<br>
my years at Adelphian Academy (had two years there before it closed),<br>
where a witnessing program was formed to give Bible Studies and neighborhood<br>
outreach to the surrounding community.<br>
<p>
All I can think of at the moment.  Keep the bios coming through - fun to read.<br>
