<i> &gt;From st0o+@andrew.cmu.edu Tue Sep 15 10:59:43 1992</i><br>
<i>&gt;From: Jeff Tosk &lt;UMBJTO@LLUVM.BITNET&gt;</i><br>
<p>
<i>&gt;</i><br>
<i>&gt;It seemed a bit odd, even disinhibited, for Steven Timm to suggest</i><br>
<i>&gt;that singles-type notices appear in the list.  Obviously when people</i><br>
<i>&gt;are in e-mail communication similarities of interest will take their</i><br>
<i>&gt;own course and singles will get acquainted.  However, the suggestion</i><br>
<i>&gt;that as a third or fourth priority this list could directly serve that</i><br>
