<title>Sep_1992: SDA-L: Another Bio...</title>
<h1>SDA-L: Another Bio...</h1>
Stan Macasieb (<i>st0o+%ANDREW.CMU.EDU%CMU.EDU@bitnet.cc.cmu.edu</i>)<br>
<i>15 Sep 1992 21:54:11 -0400</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#156">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#156">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#156">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#156">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0157.html">Jose' Luiz de Souza Gomes: "My Biography"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0155.html">Stan Macasieb: "Re: Summary of listening session"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
