<title>Sep_1992: Re: Summary of listening session</title>
<h1>Re: Summary of listening session</h1>
cheryl berthelsen (<i>cherylb@csd4.csd.uwm.edu</i>)<br>
<i>Wed, 16 Sep 92 11:27:15 -0500</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#158">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#158">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#158">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#158">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0159.html">McCluskey G: "Re: 1994"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0157.html">Jose' Luiz de Souza Gomes: "My Biography"</a>
