<title>Sep_1992: Re: 1994</title>
<h1>Re: 1994</h1>
McCluskey G (<i>glenm@usl.com</i>)<br>
<i>Wed, 16 Sep 92 13:47:42 EDT</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#159">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#159">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#159">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#159">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0160.html">Anthony Dyson: "SDA-L:  Tony's bio"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0158.html">cheryl berthelsen: "Re: Summary of listening session"</a>
<li> <b>Maybe in reply to:</b> <a href="0119.html">Steven Timm: "1994"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
