<title>Sep_1992: Another Bio...</title>
<h1>Another Bio...</h1>
Cam Litvin (<i>st0o+%ANDREW.CMU.EDU%CMU.EDU@bitnet.cc.cmu.edu</i>)<br>
<i>16 Sep 1992 21:04:15 -0400</i>
