<!-- body="start" -->
Greetings SDAnetters!<br>
<p>
I just joined the net a few weeks ago.  I'm 38 and single, but have<br>
been dating a very nice lady for the last 2.5 years.  I've worked for<br>
Tektronix in Beaverton Oregon USA since 1973.  I graduated from Laurelwood<br>
Academy also in 1973.  My job title is Telecomunications Analyst but<br>
what I really do is teach people how to use Email.  Some of my interests<br>
include computers, basketball, and bicycling.  It's been interesting<br>
seeing all of your opinions so far, and I look forward to throwing<br>
in my $ .02 worth occasinally in the future.<br>
<p>
I'd also like to take a moment to thank Steve for moderating this Net<br>
concidering the amount of time needed to read all these messages and<br>
route them on to the list.<br>
<p>
--Cam Litvin  PROFS Support  CLLITVIN<br>
