(don't make Steve redirect it all, that's unnecessary), and I'll post it to<br>
you. I won't be posting it to the SDAnet, since (a) it is 384 lines long, and<br>
(b) the topic is banned!<br>
<p>
Obviously I think this material is very worthwhile, otherwise I wouldn't have<br>
spent the last hour typing it all in for you guys... ;-)<br>
