Dear Tony,<br>
I could not tell exactly where your response originated so I can't<br>
reply personally.  However there is nothing I want to say that I wouldn't<br>
want the others to see.<br>
I very much appreciated your comments.  I too believe that the ideal for<br>
Christians is to represent God.  Although I fail daily, I would like my<br>
side of every interaction with others to reflect God's chatacter.<br>
<p>
I am going to think through a careful discussion of what I mean by<br>
an experimental relationship with God.  I would not want to be misunderstood.<br>
I'll be away for a few days.  I will write at greater length when I<br>
return ....Jeff Tosk<br>
