3:00 pm         session/s<br>
4:00 pm         Break<br>
4:30 pm         Session/s<br>
5:30 pm         Free time<br>
7:00 pm         Banquet<br>
8:30 pm         Symposium-open forum<br>
<p>
Sunday, January 31, 1993<br>
<p>
8:30 am         Devotional<br>
9:00 am         Session/s<br>
10:00 am        Free Time/Ark Expo<br>
11:00 am        Brunch Buffett<br>
4:00 pm         Ark expo ends<br>
Afternoon       Check out.<br>
<p>
Entrance Fees:<br>
