<title>Sep_1992: Re: Making the church safe for the Geritol set</title>
<h1>Re: Making the church safe for the Geritol set</h1>
Russell Yonkers (<i>st0o+@andrew.cmu.edu</i>)<br>
<i>Tue, 22 Sep 1992 21:16:19 -0400 (EDT)</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#183">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#183">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#183">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#183">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0184.html">Nancy Vyhmeister: "Re: More on translation faith"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0182.html">Tony: "Re: Making the church safe"</a>
<li> <b>In reply to:</b> <a href="0171.html">Steven Timm: "Making the church safe for the Geritol set"</a>
