<title>Sep_1992: More on translation faith</title>
<h1>More on translation faith</h1>
Ian Brown (<i>Malachi.Robertson@lambada.oit.unc.edu</i>)<br>
<i>Thu, 24 Sep 92 0:16:53 EDT</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#192">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#192">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#192">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#192">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0193.html">Fred Christiansen: "Re: More on translation faith"</a>
