Well it was close, but this is the 215th message this month to go out<br>
over SDAnet, breaking the old record of 214, set in April, '91 in the <br>
days of joint distribution.  <br>
<p>
Warren Trenchard of Canadian Union College has written to me,<br>
asking for E-mail addresses of religion teachers at SDA colleges<br>
and graduate students in religion.  I told him there were basically<br>
no people of that sort signed up to SDAnet.  But if anyone knows of some,<br>
send their addresses to me (if you think they wouldn't mind) and I<br>
will forward them to him.  This is evidently in connection with a<br>
scholarly association of Adventists whose acronyms I forget.<br>
<p>
Steve Timm<br>
